						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the basement of Saṅgamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 18th century.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Durmukhi, Vaīśākha ba. 2. The details cannot be verified.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land and house-site to the god Saṅgama by Bhōja-nāyaka.</p>						

						</summary>
